name: Demetrius Goodwin
text: This place is clearly one of the finest place in the region. Whenever I go there I am greatly happy. They hold their high  standard service and the topmost level of cooking  they give. You will be always satisfied with this restaurant. Warmly  recommended.

text: I celebrated my PhD yesterday in this great restaurant. happy to tell that we had a incredible evening and the venue was absolutely the reason for that successful meeting. The team  contributed in a graceful manner, the meals were tasty and …More

text: Wrong sauce on wrong wings, forgot marinara for breadsticks didn'tguve us our Dr. Peppe . We called, they replaced,  was even more wrong the second time. Got smart with us and hung up on us both times we called!  Won't be back …More

text: Orders $35 worth of pizza only for my order to be cancelled without notice. Not impressed one bit.

name: Ron Neitch
text: Friendly employees good people. They have been good to me and the pizza has always been good and hot. I have ordered inside and waited on my order. It was just like I wanted it. I have had them delivery and the pizza was very good and nice and hot. I don't think Google can count.

text: Have used this shop several time but whem you call and edward answers he stated and i quote you much go on line for specials. This is my sevind bad experience with edward he needs a customer service clasd if working with customer. Very sad wont be having pizza hut until management does some training. Rating -0

text: Average Pizza Hut. Simple. You get what you order. Havent had a bad pizza yet.

text: Food was good. Once I got my order right. Make sure to check your order before leaving the store.

name: Jennifer Beeson
text: Don't order from here if you want your pizza on time.  Ordered at 8 am to have pizza delivered at 11:30 am.  Still no piza at 11:45. Called and they didn't t seem to care. When we finally got it it was horrible.  Will be ordering from Casey's from now on.

name: Henry Shaner
text: Pizza cold on delivery. Forgot sauce and two liter drink.

name: justajeepgirlandherdogs
text: We order from Pizza Hut often, because it's one of the only places that deliver in Peculiar.  If there was another place, we probably would not order.  The pizza is nothing special. Its like a frozen pizza most times.  The breadsticks, garlic knots and wings are great.

name: Jose Nunez
text: Ordered online and took 15 minutes for carry out order. Pizza is very good and nicely browned. Small interior and no restroom available.

name: Will Oliver
text: Friendly staff pizza has too much sauce

name: Kayla Ragan
text: Pizza was hot when we arrived but made us the wrong pizza! Then when I mentioned it to them all she said was “we looked at it and just figured it was pepperoni and jalapeños” when what I ordered was pineapple and jalapeños. Didn’t apologize …More

text: Had fun got my food fast family loved it thanks guys
